---

---

<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-light">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-highlight font-medium text-sm tracking-wide uppercase mb-3">About</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          12 years of enterprise systems.<br />Now building the future with AI.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
          I'm Amr Sarhan — a digital transformation consultant based in Dubai who helps
          businesses replace manual processes with AI agents, intelligent automation, and
          modern systems that scale. I work across the UAE, Saudi Arabia, Egypt, and 5 other
          countries in the MENA region and beyond.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
          My career took me from Vodafone through Oracle itself, and into senior consulting
          roles leading enterprise-wide HCM and ERP transformations for government authorities,
          national banks, and multinational corporations. That foundation — understanding how
          large organizations actually operate — is what makes my AI solutions work in the real world.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Today I combine deep enterprise expertise with cutting-edge AI to build agents that
          automate HR operations, reporting pipelines, compliance workflows, and more. I don't
          just deploy technology — I architect systems that think, learn, and multiply your team's
          capacity.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">12+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-muted mt-1">Years in Enterprise</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">20+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-muted mt-1">Clients Transformed</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">8</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-muted mt-1">Countries Served</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Skills / Expertise -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-6">What I Bring</h3>
        {[
          { skill: "AI Agents & Intelligent Automation", level: "96%" },
          { skill: "Digital Transformation Strategy", level: "95%" },
          { skill: "Oracle Fusion Cloud & EBS", level: "98%" },
          { skill: "Workflow Automation & Integration", level: "94%" },
          { skill: "AI-Powered Analytics & Reporting", level: "92%" },
        ].map(({ skill, level }) => (
          <div>
            <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium text-dark">{skill}</span>
              <span class="text-muted">{level}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-2 bg-gray-200 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
              <div
                class="h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent rounded-full"
                style={`width: ${level}`}
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
